friends as many of you know, I just lost my job, at the end of September I will lose my apartment, I put these shirts on pre-sale, to be able to cover some expenses in which I find a job, as you know I love to go to shows, and if you want to donate something to be able to buy a ticket for each show, I appreciate you, I don't want to stop going to shows, anyway, I appreciate if you share this in your stories, I want to thank @killtherunts for lending me their platform and supporting me in many ways
